sub_title: Project Manager /Hydrogeology Engineer and GIS Analyst  / Cartoghrapher at Observatory of  Foggara (new opportunity)
summary: I am PhD student in Chypre International University I have  Master degree In Geology Hydrogeology Option From The University Science and Technology Houari Boumedien  -Alger, Algerie .<br>Am Looking Forward To Applying My Skills In A Practical Setting.<br>I Have Developed A Comprehensive Understanding Of Geological Mapping And The Collection Of Field Data, Coupled With The Ability To Interpret This Data And Write Detailed Reports.Hydrogeologist, Environmental Resources Management, ;Operations Management, Hydrogeologist, Terracon<br>Project Hydrogeologist / Geochemist, , ...<br><br>key Qualifications:<br><br>•	Experience in geological  Field and data Management.<br>•	Interpretation of all kind of geological and hydrogeological data related to geological reservoirs ;•	Devloped web base GIS application using ArcGis Server.<br>•	Devloped Desktop base GIS application using ArcGis Engine.<br>•	Gis technical support:  GIS Analysis ( Spatial Analyst and Geostatiscal Analyst).;•	Devloped web base GIS Interface for Water RessourceS Data.<br>•	Devloped mapping in HydroManager integraed with ArcGis Server 9.3.<br>•	Acquisition and Interpretation Geophysical data using Winsev.<br>•	Deseigned and Devloped printout Reports.<br>•	His university backround as Geologist and Hydrogeologist and his technical experience as field geologist he can play a very important to handel sever technical issues, client need understanding all aspect of project and local technical support and training.<br>•	Monitor all kind of site well operation i.e geological, drilling, Coring and wire line logging operations.<br>•	Prepare mud logs, daily reports i.e geological morninig, evening, and FWR comlection during drilling operations.<br>•	Key player during the field operation in the monitoring of groundwater quality and level and improve the management precious ressource.<br>
